\ul\b\i\fs24 About\par
\par
\ulnone\b0\i0\fs20 This program modifies "fallout2.exe" in memory for the purposes of increasing the visual resolution, playing in a window and other enhancements.\par
\par
It was compiled with "Microsoft Visual C++ Toolkit 2003" using the DirectX Oct 2006 SDK . It should work well on Windows 98 and above. And was tested using "Windows 98se", "Windows 2000 sp4", "Windows XP sp3" and "Windows 8 Pro 64bit".\par
Using this patch may require the installation of the DirectX9 redistributable package. Just download the latest version from Microsoft. This goes for Windows Vista and above users as well, as these OS's don't come with the complete DirectX9 package.\par
\par
Currently Supported versions of the "Fallout2.exe" are:\par
US 1.02d\par
UK 1.02e\par
French 1.02d\par
German 1.02d\par
Chinese 1.02?\par
Russian 'Lev Corp'\par
\par
Russian Fargus and 1C versions seem to also be compatible as the EXE's used appear to be modified from the US 1.02d version.\par
\par
