To replace the Main-menu background with a higher resolution image. Save your new FRM with the name "HR_MAINMENU.FRM" and copy it to "data\\art\\intrface". This FRM can be of any size and shape(within reason).\i\par
\i0 The "f2_res.dat" file already contains a higher resolution version of the original art at 1024x768.\par
